('0c132348-48bf-4024-9dda-7d8f056fffdf', '{"en":"SOE2K25","pa":"SOE2K25"}', '{"en":"SOE Entrance Exam 2025 Old Paper","pa":"ਸ ਓ ਈ ਪ੍ਰਵੇਸ਼ ਪ੍ਰੀਖਿਆ ੨੦੨੫"}', 180, 156, 40, NULL, TRUE, 'after_submit', 'published', '18ab2fd0-7503-457a-8ba4-d04645052a9b', '"2026-01-21T17:01:33.827Z"', '"2026-02-09T16:19:16.186Z"', '{"en":"<p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">This&nbsp;question&nbsp;paper&nbsp;is&nbsp;in&nbsp;two&nbsp;parts.</strong></p><p></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Part&nbsp;I</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;is&nbsp;related&nbsp;to&nbsp;Reasoning&nbsp;Test&nbsp;which&nbsp;consists&nbsp;of&nbsp;30&nbsp;questions.</span></p><p></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Part&nbsp;II</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;relates&nbsp;to&nbsp;Scholastic&nbsp;Aptitude&nbsp;Test&nbsp;which&nbsp;consists&nbsp;of&nbsp;120&nbsp;questions&nbsp;relating&nbsp;to&nbsp;six&nbsp;subjects&nbsp;listed&nbsp;below:</span></p><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(i)&nbsp;Mathematics&nbsp;-&nbsp;30&nbsp;questions</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(ii)&nbsp;Science&nbsp;-&nbsp;30&nbsp;questions</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(iii)&nbsp;Social&nbsp;Science&nbsp;-&nbsp;30&nbsp;questions</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(iv)&nbsp;English&nbsp;-&nbsp;10&nbsp;questions</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(v)&nbsp;Hindi&nbsp;-&nbsp;10&nbsp;questions</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(vi)&nbsp;Punjabi&nbsp;-&nbsp;10&nbsp;questions</span></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Each&nbsp;question&nbsp;carries&nbsp;1&nbsp;mark.&nbsp;There&nbsp;is&nbsp;no&nbsp;negative&nbsp;marking.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">All&nbsp;questions&nbsp;are&nbsp;compulsory.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The&nbsp;candidates&nbsp;must&nbsp;fill&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;correct&nbsp;option&nbsp;(i.e.,&nbsp;1&nbsp;or&nbsp;2&nbsp;or&nbsp;3&nbsp;or&nbsp;4)&nbsp;with&nbsp;blue/black&nbsp;ball&nbsp;point&nbsp;pen&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;OMR&nbsp;Answer&nbsp;Sheet.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The&nbsp;candidates&nbsp;should&nbsp;not&nbsp;write&nbsp;anything&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;question&nbsp;paper&nbsp;except&nbsp;his/her&nbsp;roll&nbsp;number.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The&nbsp;use&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;calculator&nbsp;or&nbsp;any&nbsp;other&nbsp;electronic&nbsp;device&nbsp;is&nbsp;strictly&nbsp;prohibited.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Rough&nbsp;work&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;done&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;space&nbsp;provided&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;end&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;question&nbsp;paper.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Hand&nbsp;over&nbsp;the&nbsp;OMR&nbsp;Answer&nbsp;Sheet&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Invigilator&nbsp;before&nbsp;leaving&nbsp;the&nbsp;examination&nbsp;hall.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">No&nbsp;candidate&nbsp;is&nbsp;allowed&nbsp;to&nbsp;leave&nbsp;the&nbsp;examination&nbsp;hall&nbsp;before&nbsp;the&nbsp;completion&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;examination&nbsp;time.</span></p>","pa":"<h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਇਹ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਪੱਤਰ&nbsp;ਦੋ&nbsp;ਭਾਗਾਂ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਹੈ।</strong></h3><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਪਹਿਲਾ&nbsp;ਭਾਗ</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;ਤਰਕ&nbsp;ਯੋਗਤਾ&nbsp;ਨਾਲ&nbsp;ਸੰਬੰਧਤ&nbsp;ਹੈ,&nbsp;ਜਿਸ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;30&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਹਨ।</span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਦੂਜੇ&nbsp;ਭਾਗ</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਵਿਸ਼ਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਦੀ&nbsp;ਯੋਗਤਾ&nbsp;ਨਾਲ&nbsp;ਸੰਬੰਧਤ&nbsp;ਨਿਮਨ&nbsp;ਦਰਸਾਏ&nbsp;ਛੇ&nbsp;ਵਿਸ਼ਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;120&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਹਨ:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(i)&nbsp;ਗਣਿਤ&nbsp;-&nbsp;30&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(ii)&nbsp;ਵਿਗਿਆਨ&nbsp;-&nbsp;30&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(iii)&nbsp;ਸਮਾਜਿਕ&nbsp;ਵਿਗਿਆਨ&nbsp;-&nbsp;30&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(iv)&nbsp;ਅੰਗਰੇਜ਼ੀ&nbsp;-&nbsp;10&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(v)&nbsp;ਹਿੰਦੀ&nbsp;-&nbsp;10&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">(vi)&nbsp;ਪੰਜਾਬੀ&nbsp;-&nbsp;10&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ</span></li></ul><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਹਰੇਕ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;1&nbsp;ਅੰਕ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਕੋਈ&nbsp;ਨਕਾਰਾਤਮਕ&nbsp;ਅੰਕ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ&nbsp;ਹੈ।</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਸਾਰੇ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਜ਼ਰੂਰੀ&nbsp;ਹਨ।</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਉਮੀਦਵਾਰ&nbsp;OMR&nbsp;ਉੱਤਰ&nbsp;ਪੱਤਰੀ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਸਹੀ&nbsp;ਵਿਕਲਪ&nbsp;(ਭਾਵ&nbsp;1&nbsp;ਜਾਂ&nbsp;2&nbsp;ਜਾਂ&nbsp;3&nbsp;ਜਾਂ&nbsp;4)&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਨੀਲੇ/ਕਾਲੇ&nbsp;ਬਾਲ&nbsp;ਪੁਆਇੰਟ&nbsp;ਪੈੱਨ&nbsp;ਨਾਲ&nbsp;ਭਰਨ।</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਉਮੀਦਵਾਰ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਪੱਤਰ&nbsp;&#39;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਆਪਣੇ&nbsp;ਰੋਲ&nbsp;ਨੰਬਰ&nbsp;ਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਇਲਾਵਾ&nbsp;ਕੁਝ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਨਾ&nbsp;ਲਿਖਣ।</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਕੈਲਕੁਲੇਟਰ&nbsp;ਜਾਂ&nbsp;ਕਿਸੇ&nbsp;ਹੋਰ&nbsp;ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਾਨਿਕ&nbsp;ਯੰਤਰ&nbsp;ਦੀ&nbsp;ਵਰਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਦੀ&nbsp;ਸਖ਼ਤ&nbsp;ਮਨਾਹੀ&nbsp;ਹੈ।</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਕੱਚਾ&nbsp;ਕੰਮ&nbsp;(Rough&nbsp;work)&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਪੱਤਰ&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਅੰਤ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਦਿੱਤੀ&nbsp;ਗਈ&nbsp;ਖਾਲੀ&nbsp;ਥਾਂ&nbsp;&#39;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਕੀਤਾ&nbsp;ਜਾ&nbsp;ਸਕਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ।</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਪ੍ਰੀਖਿਆ&nbsp;ਹਾਲ&nbsp;ਛੱਡਣ&nbsp;ਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਪਹਿਲਾਂ&nbsp;OMR&nbsp;ਉੱਤਰ&nbsp;ਪੱਤਰੀ&nbsp;ਨਿਗਰਾਨ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਸੌਂਪ&nbsp;ਦਿਓ।</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਪ੍ਰੀਖਿਆ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਸਮਾਂ&nbsp;ਖਤਮ&nbsp;ਹੋਣ&nbsp;ਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਪਹਿਲਾਂ&nbsp;ਕਿਸੇ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਉਮੀਦਵਾਰ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰੀਖਿਆ&nbsp;ਹਾਲ&nbsp;ਛੱਡਣ&nbsp;ਦੀ&nbsp;ਇਜਾਜ਼ਤ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ&nbsp;ਹੈ।</span></p>"}', FALSE, TRUE, 3);
