INSERT INTO "paragraphs" ("id", "text", "content", "image_url", "created_at", "updated_at") VALUES
('fae33b00-945e-4671-9542-076456f56cf5', '{"en":"Chandigarh Architecture – Comprehension Passage","pa":"ਚੰਡੀਗੜ ਦਾ ਆਰਕੀਟੈਕਚਰ - ਲੇਖ"}', '{"en":"<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Chandigarh&nbsp;is&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;well-planned&nbsp;cities&nbsp;in&nbsp;India&nbsp;and&nbsp;is&nbsp;world-famous&nbsp;for&nbsp;its&nbsp;unique&nbsp;and&nbsp;modern&nbsp;architecture.&nbsp;After&nbsp;India&nbsp;gained&nbsp;independence&nbsp;in&nbsp;1947,&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;was&nbsp;designed&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;capital&nbsp;of&nbsp;Punjab.&nbsp;The&nbsp;responsibility&nbsp;of&nbsp;planning&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;was&nbsp;given&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;renowned&nbsp;French&nbsp;architect&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Le&nbsp;Corbusier</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">,&nbsp;who&nbsp;shaped&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;symbol&nbsp;of&nbsp;modern&nbsp;India.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;of&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;is&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;principles&nbsp;of&nbsp;modernism.&nbsp;Buildings&nbsp;are&nbsp;simple,&nbsp;functional,&nbsp;and&nbsp;free&nbsp;from&nbsp;excessive&nbsp;decoration.&nbsp;Concrete,&nbsp;straight&nbsp;lines,&nbsp;bold&nbsp;shapes,&nbsp;and&nbsp;open&nbsp;spaces&nbsp;are&nbsp;the&nbsp;main&nbsp;features.&nbsp;The&nbsp;city&nbsp;is&nbsp;divided&nbsp;into&nbsp;well-organized&nbsp;sectors,&nbsp;each&nbsp;planned&nbsp;for&nbsp;specific&nbsp;purposes&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;living,&nbsp;shopping,&nbsp;education,&nbsp;and&nbsp;recreation.&nbsp;This&nbsp;systematic&nbsp;layout&nbsp;makes&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;easy&nbsp;to&nbsp;navigate&nbsp;and&nbsp;highly&nbsp;efficient.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Some&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;structures&nbsp;in&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;are&nbsp;the&nbsp;Capitol&nbsp;Complex&nbsp;buildings,&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;High&nbsp;Court,&nbsp;Secretariat,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Legislative&nbsp;Assembly.&nbsp;These&nbsp;buildings&nbsp;reflect&nbsp;strength,&nbsp;order,&nbsp;and&nbsp;clarity.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Open&nbsp;Hand&nbsp;Monument,&nbsp;another&nbsp;famous&nbsp;structure,&nbsp;represents&nbsp;peace&nbsp;and&nbsp;unity,&nbsp;showing&nbsp;Corbusier’s&nbsp;belief&nbsp;in&nbsp;giving&nbsp;and&nbsp;receiving&nbsp;freely.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Apart&nbsp;from&nbsp;official&nbsp;buildings,&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;also&nbsp;blends&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;with&nbsp;nature.&nbsp;Wide&nbsp;roads,&nbsp;green&nbsp;belts,&nbsp;parks,&nbsp;and&nbsp;gardens&nbsp;are&nbsp;carefully&nbsp;planned&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;a&nbsp;clean&nbsp;and&nbsp;healthy&nbsp;environment.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Rock&nbsp;Garden,&nbsp;created&nbsp;from&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;and&nbsp;household&nbsp;waste,&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;creative&nbsp;example&nbsp;of&nbsp;sustainable&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;and&nbsp;artistic&nbsp;expression.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Overall,&nbsp;Chandigarh’s&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;stands&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;landmark&nbsp;in&nbsp;Indian&nbsp;urban&nbsp;planning.&nbsp;It&nbsp;combines&nbsp;functionality,&nbsp;aesthetics,&nbsp;and&nbsp;harmony&nbsp;with&nbsp;nature,&nbsp;making&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;a&nbsp;timeless&nbsp;example&nbsp;of&nbsp;thoughtful&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;modern&nbsp;vision.</span></p><p></p><p></p>","pa":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Chandigarh&nbsp;is&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;well-planned&nbsp;cities&nbsp;in&nbsp;India&nbsp;and&nbsp;is&nbsp;world-famous&nbsp;for&nbsp;its&nbsp;unique&nbsp;and&nbsp;modern&nbsp;architecture.&nbsp;After&nbsp;India&nbsp;gained&nbsp;independence&nbsp;in&nbsp;1947,&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;was&nbsp;designed&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;capital&nbsp;of&nbsp;Punjab.&nbsp;The&nbsp;responsibility&nbsp;of&nbsp;planning&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;was&nbsp;given&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;renowned&nbsp;French&nbsp;architect&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Le&nbsp;Corbusier</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,&nbsp;who&nbsp;shaped&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;symbol&nbsp;of&nbsp;modern&nbsp;India.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;of&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;is&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;principles&nbsp;of&nbsp;modernism.&nbsp;Buildings&nbsp;are&nbsp;simple,&nbsp;functional,&nbsp;and&nbsp;free&nbsp;from&nbsp;excessive&nbsp;decoration.&nbsp;Concrete,&nbsp;straight&nbsp;lines,&nbsp;bold&nbsp;shapes,&nbsp;and&nbsp;open&nbsp;spaces&nbsp;are&nbsp;the&nbsp;main&nbsp;features.&nbsp;The&nbsp;city&nbsp;is&nbsp;divided&nbsp;into&nbsp;well-organized&nbsp;sectors,&nbsp;each&nbsp;planned&nbsp;for&nbsp;specific&nbsp;purposes&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;living,&nbsp;shopping,&nbsp;education,&nbsp;and&nbsp;recreation.&nbsp;This&nbsp;systematic&nbsp;layout&nbsp;makes&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;easy&nbsp;to&nbsp;navigate&nbsp;and&nbsp;highly&nbsp;efficient.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Some&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;structures&nbsp;in&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;are&nbsp;the&nbsp;Capitol&nbsp;Complex&nbsp;buildings,&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;High&nbsp;Court,&nbsp;Secretariat,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Legislative&nbsp;Assembly.&nbsp;These&nbsp;buildings&nbsp;reflect&nbsp;strength,&nbsp;order,&nbsp;and&nbsp;clarity.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Open&nbsp;Hand&nbsp;Monument,&nbsp;another&nbsp;famous&nbsp;structure,&nbsp;represents&nbsp;peace&nbsp;and&nbsp;unity,&nbsp;showing&nbsp;Corbusier’s&nbsp;belief&nbsp;in&nbsp;giving&nbsp;and&nbsp;receiving&nbsp;freely.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Apart&nbsp;from&nbsp;official&nbsp;buildings,&nbsp;Chandigarh&nbsp;also&nbsp;blends&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;with&nbsp;nature.&nbsp;Wide&nbsp;roads,&nbsp;green&nbsp;belts,&nbsp;parks,&nbsp;and&nbsp;gardens&nbsp;are&nbsp;carefully&nbsp;planned&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;a&nbsp;clean&nbsp;and&nbsp;healthy&nbsp;environment.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Rock&nbsp;Garden,&nbsp;created&nbsp;from&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;and&nbsp;household&nbsp;waste,&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;creative&nbsp;example&nbsp;of&nbsp;sustainable&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;and&nbsp;artistic&nbsp;expression.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Overall,&nbsp;Chandigarh’s&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;stands&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;landmark&nbsp;in&nbsp;Indian&nbsp;urban&nbsp;planning.&nbsp;It&nbsp;combines&nbsp;functionality,&nbsp;aesthetics,&nbsp;and&nbsp;harmony&nbsp;with&nbsp;nature,&nbsp;making&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;a&nbsp;timeless&nbsp;example&nbsp;of&nbsp;thoughtful&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;modern&nbsp;vision.</span></p><p></p>"}', NULL, '"2026-01-26T10:39:03.756Z"', '"2026-01-26T11:48:16.660Z"'),
('3e1c5378-6d8f-41a9-b908-074dab9ed545', '{"en":"Social Media","pa":"Social Media"}', '{"en":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Social&nbsp;media&nbsp;has&nbsp;changed&nbsp;the&nbsp;way&nbsp;we&nbsp;communicate,&nbsp;interact&nbsp;and&nbsp;share&nbsp;information.&nbsp;Online&nbsp;platforms&nbsp;like&nbsp;Facebook,&nbsp;Twitter,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Instagram&nbsp;have&nbsp;become&nbsp;an&nbsp;important&nbsp;part&nbsp;of&nbsp;our&nbsp;daily&nbsp;lives.&nbsp;Social&nbsp;media&nbsp;has&nbsp;made&nbsp;it&nbsp;easier&nbsp;for&nbsp;people&nbsp;to&nbsp;connect&nbsp;with&nbsp;each&nbsp;other&nbsp;from&nbsp;anywhere&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world.&nbsp;It&nbsp;has&nbsp;also&nbsp;enabled&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;companies&nbsp;to&nbsp;reach&nbsp;more&nbsp;people&nbsp;and&nbsp;promote&nbsp;their&nbsp;products&nbsp;more&nbsp;effectively.&nbsp;Moreover,&nbsp;social&nbsp;media&nbsp;has&nbsp;enabled&nbsp;people&nbsp;to&nbsp;spread&nbsp;good&nbsp;messages&nbsp;and&nbsp;also&nbsp;raise&nbsp;awareness&nbsp;about&nbsp;social&nbsp;issues.&nbsp;For&nbsp;students,&nbsp;social&nbsp;media&nbsp;offers&nbsp;numerous&nbsp;benefits.&nbsp;It&nbsp;serves&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;valuable&nbsp;resource&nbsp;for&nbsp;learning&nbsp;enabling&nbsp;access&nbsp;to&nbsp;educational&nbsp;videos,&nbsp;online&nbsp;courses,&nbsp;and&nbsp;expert&nbsp;opinions.&nbsp;However,&nbsp;social&nbsp;media&nbsp;has&nbsp;some&nbsp;negative&nbsp;impacts&nbsp;as&nbsp;well.&nbsp;Excessive&nbsp;use&nbsp;of&nbsp;social&nbsp;media&nbsp;leads&nbsp;to&nbsp;addiction,&nbsp;wasting&nbsp;valuable&nbsp;time&nbsp;that&nbsp;could&nbsp;be&nbsp;spent&nbsp;on&nbsp;productive&nbsp;activities&nbsp;and&nbsp;declining&nbsp;face-to-face&nbsp;conversation&nbsp;with&nbsp;people.&nbsp;It&nbsp;also&nbsp;causes&nbsp;physical&nbsp;and&nbsp;mental&nbsp;health&nbsp;problems.&nbsp;The&nbsp;spread&nbsp;of&nbsp;fake&nbsp;news&nbsp;and&nbsp;misinformation&nbsp;misleads&nbsp;people&nbsp;and&nbsp;creates&nbsp;confusion.&nbsp;To&nbsp;sum&nbsp;up,&nbsp;social&nbsp;media&nbsp;is&nbsp;like&nbsp;a&nbsp;double-edged&nbsp;sword&nbsp;-&nbsp;It&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;really&nbsp;helpful&nbsp;or&nbsp;harmful&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;how&nbsp;people&nbsp;use&nbsp;it.&nbsp;Undoubtedly,&nbsp;it&nbsp;provides&nbsp;amazing&nbsp;chances&nbsp;for&nbsp;learning,&nbsp;connecting&nbsp;with&nbsp;others&nbsp;and&nbsp;sharing&nbsp;ideas.&nbsp;At&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;time,&nbsp;it&nbsp;requires&nbsp;careful&nbsp;management&nbsp;to&nbsp;avoid&nbsp;its&nbsp;negative&nbsp;effects.&nbsp;By&nbsp;using&nbsp;social&nbsp;media&nbsp;wisely&nbsp;and&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;clear&nbsp;purpose,&nbsp;we&nbsp;can&nbsp;leverage&nbsp;its&nbsp;benefits&nbsp;while&nbsp;minimizing&nbsp;its&nbsp;drawbacks,&nbsp;making&nbsp;it&nbsp;a&nbsp;tool&nbsp;for&nbsp;personal&nbsp;growth&nbsp;and&nbsp;social&nbsp;progress.</span></p>","pa":"Social media has changed the way we communicate, interact and share information. Online platforms like Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram have become an important part of our daily lives... However, social media has some negative impacts as well... To sum up, social media is like a double-edged sword..."}', NULL, '"2026-01-26T16:30:19.713Z"', '"2026-01-26T16:46:51.480Z"'),
('c82969c4-195e-4bba-afa5-99948ff5c39c', '{"en":"ਸੱਭਿਅਤਾ","pa":"ਸੱਭਿਅਤਾ"}', '{"en":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ਸੱਭਿਅਤਾ&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਜਨਮ&nbsp;ਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਹੀ&nbsp;ਇਹ&nbsp;ਮਹਿਸੂਸ&nbsp;ਕੀਤਾ&nbsp;ਜਾਂਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ&nbsp;ਕਿ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਦਿਆ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਉਦੇਸ਼&nbsp;ਪਰਉਪਕਾਰ&nbsp;ਕਰਨਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਇਸ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਮੰਤਵ&nbsp;ਗਿਆਨ&nbsp;ਦੇਣਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ,&nbsp;ਕਿਤਾਬੀ-ਕੀੜਾ&nbsp;ਬਣਾਉਣਾ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ,&nbsp;ਅਗਿਆਨ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਹਨੇਰਾ&nbsp;ਦੂਰ&nbsp;ਕਰਨਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ,&nbsp;ਨਿਰੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਕਾਗ਼ਜ਼ੀ&nbsp;ਡਿਗਰੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਵੰਡਣਾ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ,&nbsp;ਦੂਸਰੇ&nbsp;ਸ਼ਬਦਾਂ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਮਨੁੱਖ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਵਾਸਤਵਿਕ&nbsp;ਸਮਾਜਿਕ&nbsp;ਜੀਵ&nbsp;ਬਣਾਉਣਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਰੁਜ਼ਗਾਰ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤੀ&nbsp;ਉਸ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਦੂਜਾ&nbsp;ਪਹਿਲੂ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਗਿਆਨ&nbsp;ਸਮਾਜਿਕ,&nbsp;ਰਾਜਨੀਤਿਕ,&nbsp;ਆਰਥਿਕ,&nbsp;ਭੂਗੋਲਿਕ,&nbsp;ਇਤਿਹਾਸਿਕ,&nbsp;ਸਾਹਿਤਕ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਵਿਗਿਆਨਿਕ&nbsp;ਆਦਿ&nbsp;ਹੋ&nbsp;ਸਕਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਇਹ&nbsp;ਗਿਆਨ,&nbsp;ਨਿਰਸੰਦੇਹ,&nbsp;ਕਿਤਾਬਾਂ&nbsp;ਰਾਹੀਂ&nbsp;ਗ੍ਰਹਿਣ&nbsp;ਕੀਤਾ&nbsp;ਜਾ&nbsp;ਸਕਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ,&nbsp;ਭਾਵੇਂ&nbsp;ਅੱਜ-ਕੁੱਲ੍ਹ&nbsp;ਰੇਡੀਓ,&nbsp;ਟੈਲੀਵੀਜ਼ਨ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਸਿਨੇਮਾ&nbsp;ਆਦਿ&nbsp;ਨਵੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਵਿਧੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਦੀ&nbsp;ਵਰਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਕੀਤੀ&nbsp;ਜਾ&nbsp;ਰਹੀ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਪੜ੍ਹੇ-ਲਿਖੇ&nbsp;ਨੌਜਵਾਨ&nbsp;ਵਿਸ਼ਾਦ&nbsp;(ਨਿਰਾਸ਼ਾ)&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਡੂੰਘੇ&nbsp;ਸਾਗਰ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਡੁੱਬੇ&nbsp;ਹੋਏ&nbsp;ਹਨ।&nbsp;ਵਾਸਤਵ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਅੰਗਰੇਜ਼ਾਂ&nbsp;ਨੇ&nbsp;ਆਪਣੀ&nbsp;ਕਲਰਕ-ਲੋੜ-ਪੂਰਤੀ&nbsp;ਲਈ&nbsp;&#39;ਕਲਰਕ&nbsp;ਬਣਾਓ&#39;&nbsp;ਵਿੱਦਿਅਕ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਨਾਲੀ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਚਲਿਤ&nbsp;ਕੀਤੀ&nbsp;ਸੀ,&nbsp;ਪਰ&nbsp;ਦੁੱਖ&nbsp;ਦੀ&nbsp;ਗੱਲ&nbsp;ਹੈ&nbsp;ਕਿ&nbsp;ਅੱਜ&nbsp;ਪੰਜ&nbsp;ਦਹਾਕਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਬਾਅਦ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਇਹੀ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਨਾਲੀ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਚਲਨ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਜੋ&nbsp;ਅਸਲ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਦਿਆ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਉਸ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਚਾਨਣ&nbsp;ਮਨੁੱਖੀ&nbsp;ਆਚਰਨ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਉੱਚਾ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਸੁੱਚਾ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਬਣਾਉਂਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਉਸ&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਦਿਲ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਦੁਖੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਲਈ&nbsp;ਦਰਦ,&nbsp;ਜ਼ਾਲਮਾਂ&nbsp;ਵਿਰੁੱਧ&nbsp;ਵਿਦਰੋਹ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਝੂਠਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰਤੀ&nbsp;ਘਿਰਨਾ&nbsp;ਪੈਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੁੰਦੀ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਜੇ&nbsp;ਕੋਈ&nbsp;ਪੜ੍ਹ-ਲਿਖ&nbsp;ਕੇ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਪੰਜੇ&nbsp;ਐਬਾਂ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਗ਼ਲਤਾਨ&nbsp;ਰਹਿੰਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ,&nbsp;ਦੋਖੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਸਜ਼ਾ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ&nbsp;ਦਿੰਦਾ,&nbsp;ਸੱਚ-ਝੂਠ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਨਿਤਾਰਾ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ&nbsp;ਕਰਦਾ,&nbsp;ਅਨਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਵਿਰੁੱਧ&nbsp;ਕੁੰਡਾ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ&nbsp;ਖੜਕਾਉਂਦਾ,&nbsp;ਜਨਤਾ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਕੁਝ&nbsp;ਸਵਾਰਦਾ&nbsp;ਨਹੀਂ&nbsp;ਤਾਂ&nbsp;ਉਹਦੀ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਦਿਆ&nbsp;ਜਿਹੀ&nbsp;ਹੋਈ&nbsp;ਤਿਹੀ&nbsp;ਨਾ&nbsp;ਹੋਈ&#39;।&nbsp;ਵਿੱਦਿਆ&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਸਰਬ-ਪੱਖੀ&nbsp;ਵਿਕਾਸ&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਮਨੋਰਥ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਮੁੱਖ&nbsp;ਰੱਖਦਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਹੋਇਆਂ&nbsp;ਵਿਦਿਆਲਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਪੜ੍ਹਾਈ&nbsp;ਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਛੁੱਟ&nbsp;ਖੇਡਾਂ,&nbsp;ਮਨੋਰੰਜਨ&nbsp;ਕਾਰਜਾਂ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਧਾਰਮਿਕ&nbsp;ਸਿੱਖਿਆ&nbsp;ਵੱਲ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਵਿਸ਼ੇਸ਼&nbsp;ਧਿਆਨ&nbsp;ਦਿੱਤਾ&nbsp;ਜਾਂਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ।&nbsp;ਵਿਦਿਆਰਥੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਨਿਸ਼ਚਿਤ&nbsp;ਪਾਠ-ਕ੍ਰਮ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਅਧਾਰਿਤ&nbsp;ਪੁਸਤਕਾਂ&nbsp;ਪੜ੍ਹਾਈਆਂ&nbsp;ਜਾਂਦੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਹਨ&nbsp;ਤਾਂ&nbsp;ਜੋ&nbsp;ਉਹ&nbsp;ਮਾਨਸਿਕ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਬੌਧਿਕ&nbsp;ਵਿਕਾਸ&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਨਾਲ-ਨਾਲ&nbsp;ਯੂਨੀਵਰਸਿਟੀ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਇਮਤਿਹਾਨ&nbsp;ਵੀ&nbsp;ਪਾਸ&nbsp;ਕਰ&nbsp;ਸਕਣ।&nbsp;ਉਹਨਾਂ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਵਿਭਿੰਨ&nbsp;ਖੇਡਾਂ&nbsp;ਖਿਡਾਈਆਂ&nbsp;ਜਾਂਦੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਹਨ&nbsp;ਤਾਂ&nbsp;ਜੋ&nbsp;ਉਹ&nbsp;ਸਿਹਤਮੰਦ&nbsp;ਰਹਿ&nbsp;ਸਕਣ।&nbsp;ਉਹਨਾਂ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਭਾਸ਼ਨ,&nbsp;ਸੰਗੀਤ,&nbsp;ਨਾਟਕ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਲਲਿਤ&nbsp;ਕਲਾ&nbsp;ਆਦਿ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਗਿਆਨ&nbsp;ਦਿੱਤਾ&nbsp;ਜਾਂਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ&nbsp;ਤਾਂ&nbsp;ਜੋ&nbsp;ਉਹ&nbsp;ਆਪਣੇ&nbsp;ਵਿਅਕਤੀਤਵ&nbsp;ਦਾ&nbsp;ਬਹੁ-ਪੱਖੀ&nbsp;ਵਿਕਾਸ&nbsp;ਕਰ&nbsp;ਸਕਣ।&nbsp;ਉਹਨਾਂ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਧਾਰਮਿਕ&nbsp;ਸਿੱਖਿਆ&nbsp;ਦਿੱਤੀ&nbsp;ਜਾਂਦੀ&nbsp;ਹੈ&nbsp;ਤਾਂ&nbsp;ਜੋ&nbsp;ਉਹ&nbsp;ਅਦਿੱਖ,&nbsp;ਅਪਾਰ&nbsp;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਬੇਅੰਤ&nbsp;ਸ਼ਕਤੀ&nbsp;ਤੋਂ&nbsp;ਡਰ&nbsp;ਕੇ&nbsp;ਰਹਿਣ,&nbsp;ਨਿਰੀ&nbsp;&#39;ਹਉਂਮੈਂ&#39;&nbsp;ਦੇ&nbsp;ਝਗੜਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਆਪਣਾ&nbsp;ਸਮਾਂ&nbsp;ਅਜਾਈਂ&nbsp;ਨਾ&nbsp;ਗੁਆਉਣ।&nbsp;ਉਹਨਾਂ&nbsp;ਨੂੰ&nbsp;ਧਾਰਮਿਕ&nbsp;ਗ੍ਰੰਥਾਂ&nbsp;ਵਿੱਚ&nbsp;ਦਿੱਤੀਆਂ&nbsp;ਹੋਈਆਂ&nbsp;ਸਿੱਖਿਆਵਾਂ&nbsp;&#39;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਅਮਲ&nbsp;ਅਤੇ&nbsp;ਅਵਤਾਰਾਂ,&nbsp;ਪੀਰਾਂ-ਪੈਗੰਬਰਾਂ&nbsp;ਦਿਆਂ&nbsp;ਪੂਰਨਿਆਂ&nbsp;&#39;ਤੇ&nbsp;ਚਲਣ&nbsp;ਲਈ&nbsp;ਪ੍ਰੇਰਿਆ&nbsp;ਜਾਂਦਾ&nbsp;ਹੈ।</span></p>","pa":"ਸੱਭਿਅਤਾ ਦੇ ਜਨਮ ਤੋਂ ਹੀ ਇਹ ਮਹਿਸੂਸ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ ਕਿ ਵਿੱਦਿਆ ਦਾ ਉਦੇਸ਼ ਪਰਉਪਕਾਰ ਕਰਨਾ ਹੈ। ਇਸ ਦਾ ਮੰਤਵ ਗਿਆਨ ਦੇਣਾ ਹੈ, ਕਿਤਾਬੀ-ਕੀੜਾ ਬਣਾਉਣਾ ਨਹੀਂ, ਅਗਿਆਨ ਦਾ ਹਨੇਰਾ ਦੂਰ ਕਰਨਾ ਹੈ, ਨਿਰੀਆਂ ਕਾਗ਼ਜ਼ੀ ਡਿਗਰੀਆਂ ਵੰਡਣ