('900e16e3-310a-44d1-a7d6-fb8759582313', '150bbc38-362e-46ef-a965-8ee8349c3bfa', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"Choose the correct alternative that will continue the same pattern and replace the question mark (?) in the given series: 3, 10, 101, ?","pa":"ਪੈਟਰਨ ਨੂੰ ਜਾਰੀ ਰੱਖਣ ਲਈ ਸਹੀ ਵਿਕਲਪ ਚੁਣੋ ਅਤੇ ਦਿੱਤੀ ਹੋਈ ਲੜੀ ਵਿੱਚੋਂ ''?'' ਦੀ ਜਗ੍ਹਾ ਤੇ ਲਿਖੋ: 3, 10, 101, ?"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"10101","pa":"10101"}},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"10201","pa":"10201"}},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"10202","pa":"10202"}},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"11012","pa":"11012"}}]', '["c"]', '{"en":"The pattern is n² + 1. 3²+1=10, 10²+1=101. Next term is 101²+1 = 10201+1 = 10202.","pa":"ਪੈਟਰਨ n² + 1 ਹੈ। 3²+1=10, 10²+1=101. ਅਗਲਾ ਪਦ 101²+1 = 10201+1 = 10202 ਹੋਵੇਗਾ।"}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 4, NULL, NULL, 4, NULL),
('c578bea1-a83b-4373-a49e-fda1bc26db8e', 'f4d9390b-b4a5-4387-b1d8-5a033627b550', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"If in the figure, BC is the diameter, radius of circle is 5 cm and AB = 6 cm, then AC is:","pa":"ਜੇਕਰ ਚਿੱਤਰ ਵਿੱਚ BC ਵਿਆਸ ਹੈ, ਚੱਕਰ ਦਾ ਅਰਧਵਿਆਸ 5 cm ਹੈ ਅਤੇ AB = 6 cm ਤਾਂ AC ਬਰਾਬਰ ਹੈ:"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"8 cm","pa":"8 cm"}},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"11 cm","pa":"11 cm"}},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"10 cm","pa":"10 cm"}},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"30 cm","pa":"30 cm"}}]', '["a"]', '{"en":"Diameter BC = 10cm. Angle in semicircle A is 90°. By Pythagoras: AC = √(10² - 6²) = √(100-36) = √64 = 8.","pa":"ਵਿਆਸ BC = 10cm. ਅਰਧ ਚੱਕਰ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੋਣ A 90° ਹੈ। ਪਾਇਥਾਗੋਰਸ ਦੁਆਰਾ: AC = √(10² - 6²) = √(100-36) = √64 = 8."}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 14, NULL, NULL, 4, NULL),
('58770ec4-57f1-4255-8ccc-44f0347c1733', 'f4d9390b-b4a5-4387-b1d8-5a033627b550', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"Which of the following is true?","pa":"ਹੇਠ ਲਿਖੇ ਵਿੱਚੋਂ ਕਿਹੜਾ ਸਹੀ ਹੈ ?"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"sin²θ + tan²(90°-θ) = 1","pa":"sin²θ + tan²(90°-θ) = 1"}},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"cos²θ + cos²(90°-θ) = 1","pa":"cos²θ + cos²(90°-θ) = 1"}},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"sin²θ + cos²θ = 0","pa":"sin²θ + cos²θ = 0"}},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"sec²θ - sec²(90°-θ) = 1","pa":"sec²θ - sec²(90°-θ) = 1"}}]', '["b"]', '{"en":"cos²(90°-θ) = sin²θ. So cos²θ + sin²θ = 1, which is a standard identity.","pa":"cos²(90°-θ) = sin²θ. ਇਸ ਲਈ cos²θ + sin²θ = 1, ਜੋ ਕਿ ਇੱਕ ਮਿਆਰੀ ਪਛਾਣ ਹੈ।"}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 17, NULL, NULL, 4, NULL),
('9d25fb81-1866-401c-96cb-c57b59cceef0', 'f4d9390b-b4a5-4387-b1d8-5a033627b550', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"If roots of a quadratic equation are 4 and -3, then the quadratic equation is:","pa":"ਜੇਕਰ ਇੱਕ ਦੋ ਘਾਤੀ ਸਮੀਕਰਣ ਦੇ ਮੂਲ 4 ਅਤੇ -3 ਹਨ ਤਾਂ ਦੋ ਘਾਤੀ ਸਮੀਕਰਣ ਹੈ :"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"x² - x - 12 = 0","pa":"x² - x - 12 = 0"}},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"x² + x - 12 = 0","pa":"x² + x - 12 = 0"}},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"x² + 7x - 12 = 0","pa":"x² + 7x - 12 = 0"}},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"x² - 7x + 12 = 0","pa":"x² - 7x + 12 = 0"}}]', '["a"]', '{"en":"Sum of roots = 4 + (-3) = 1. Product = 4 * (-3) = -12. Eq: x² - (sum)x + product = 0 => x² - x - 12 = 0.","pa":"ਮੂਲ ਦਾ ਜੋੜ = 1. ਗੁਣਨਫਲ = -12. ਸਮੀਕਰਣ: x² - (ਜੋੜ)x + ਗੁਣਨਫਲ = 0 => x² - x - 12 = 0."}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 22, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
('9fbd2cee-71ec-4c34-9b76-d202b36984e2', 'f4d9390b-b4a5-4387-b1d8-5a033627b550', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"If ''a'' is the first term of an arithmetic progression and Sₙ = 2aₙ, then:","pa":"ਜੇਕਰ ਇੱਕ ਅੰਕ ਗਣਿਤਕ ਲੜੀ ਵਿੱਚ ''a'' ਪਹਿਲਾ ਪਦ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ Sₙ = 2aₙ ਹੈ, ਤਾਂ:"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"aₙ = 3a","pa":"aₙ = 3a "},"image_url":null},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"3aₙ  = na","pa":"3aₙ  = na"},"image_url":null},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"(4-n)aₙ  = na","pa":"(4-n)aₙ  = na"},"image_url":null},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"5aₙ  = a","pa":"5aₙ  = a"},"image_url":null}]', '["c"]', '{"en":"Sₙ = (n/2)(a + aₙ). Given Sn = 2aₙ. So, 2aₙ = (n/2)(a + aₙ) => 4aₙ= na + naₙ => 4aₙ - naₙ = na => aₙ(4-n) = na.","pa":"Sn = (n/2)(a + an). ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ Sn = 2an. ਇਸ ਲਈ, 2an = (n/2)(a + an) => 4an = na + nan => 4an - nan = na => an(4-n) = na."}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL),
